snippet.title: NES Longplay [129] Chip 'n Dale: Rescue Rangers 2 (2P)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by:  Tsunao & Genbu

Platformer by friggin' Capcom.

Fat Cat is out of prison or something and Ch-ch-ch-Chip 'n Dale (Rescue Rangers) are at it again...or something. I skipped the cutscenes because they bore me.

I control Chip (Player 1) while bro controls Dale (Player 2). No skills involved. Deaths here and there because two-player makes the game harder (and perfect gameplays are BORING! Needz moar deaths). -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
